=John M. Crawford, Jr. (1913-1988)=
==Literature==
===Monographs===
* Wango H.C. Weng: Chinese Painting and Calligraphy: A Pictorial Survey: 69 Fine Examples from the John M. Crawford, Jr Collection. New York: Dover Publications, 1978
* Kwan S. Wong and Stephen Addiss: Masterpieces of Sung and Yuan Dynasty Calligraphy from the John M. Crawford, Jr Collection. New York: China House Gallery, 1981 